subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: What is the famous palace associated with Maharaja Sawai Man Singh II?
question_hi: महाराजा सवाई सावकी मंसूर सिंह एक्स्पेक्टोरेशंस का फोटोपेक्षात्मक पालक का नाम है।
explanation_en:
Amer Fort and Kumbhalgarh Fort are both historic forts in Rajasthan, but the famous photographically stable palace associated with Maharaja Sawai Mansingh II is Kumbhalgarh Fort.
